## рџ§  Risk Scoring Algorithm

Each scanned network is scored 0вЂ“100:

| Condition                          | Points |
|------------------------------------|--------|
| Duplicate SSID (different BSSID)   | +40    |
| Open / no encryption               | +20    |
| WEP encryption (broken since 2001) | +15    |
| Signal > -45 dBm (boosted rogue)   | +15    |
| Unknown/rogue vendor               | +25    |
| Known SSID + weak encryption       | +15    |
| Rogue OUI prefix in BSSID          | +10    |

**Risk Levels:** LOW (0вЂ“34) В· MEDIUM (35вЂ“59) В· HIGH (60вЂ“79) В· CRITICAL (80вЂ“100)

