## рџ”ђ Security Features

- **JWT Authentication** вЂ” 7-day expiry, role-based (user/admin)
- **bcrypt** вЂ” Password hashing with salt rounds = 12
- **Rate Limiting** вЂ” 200 requests / 15 minutes per IP
- **Input Validation** вЂ” Length limits, enum validation, sanitization
- **CORS** вЂ” Configurable origin restrictions
- **Role Guards** вЂ” Admin routes protected with `authorize('admin')` middleware

